Package: add-desktop
Architecture: amd64
Version: 0.3.18-1
Maintainer: Andreas Mueller <amu@gnoppix.com>
Description: Add Desktop - Electron GUI client for Add messenger
 Electron-based desktop client with Signal-inspired interface for Add
 post-quantum encrypted messaging.
 .
 Features:
  - Split-pane interface (sidebar + chat)
  - Real-time message delivery
  - TTL auto-destruct timer (2h, 12h, 24h, 48h, 5d, 7d, 14d)
  - Emoji picker integration
  - Reflector Bot for latency testing
Depends: libnss3, libatk1.0-0, libatk-bridge2.0-0, libcups2, libdrm2, libxkbcommon0, libxcomposite1, libxdamage1, libxrandr2, libgbm1, libasound2, libpangocairo-1.0-0, libpango-1.0-0, libgtk-3-0, libtss2-esys-3.0.2-0, libtss2-tctildr0t64
Section: net
Priority: optional
